summary: AN ORDINANCE approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6379 for the improvement of The Alley in block 33, (Plat of the) Town of Seattle as laid out by D. S. Maynard, being the alley between 5th Avenue South and 6th Avenue South from South Jackson Street to South Main Street; and a certain other alley; by paving and otherwise improving the same.
